data.description: FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN! Forsyth County Schools! Just a short walk to LANIER! This AMAZING Like-New home is next to over 200+ acres of US Corp land! Come see this beautiful 4 bedroom / 2.5 bath home with a basement today! Kitchen boosts Granite Countertops, White Painted Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances, Breakfast room, and the Kitchen opens to a nice sized deck. The main has GORGEOUS LVP Floors, spacious living room, and separate dining room. Nice half bath on main. Upstairs has a LARGE master bedroom w/tray ceiling, master bath flooring is LPV, w/tiled shower, double vanity, and walk-in closet. Upstairs has THREE nice size rooms. Also, has a Full bath with a double vanity & separate laundry room. The unfinished basement is stubbed for a bathroom. Enjoy this Quiet community from the front porch. Neighborhood amenities include a pool, tennis court, playground, & basketball court. Great Schools & Great Location! Just a short drive away you'll find, shopping, dining, Keith Bridge Park and Convenient to GA 400 & I-985!
